snippet.title: Arena Breakout: Infinite Full Release Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
The Arena Breakout: Infinite full release is coming at the end of 2024!
Watch the Full Release Announcement Trailer from #OpeningNightLive2024, and visit our gamescom 2024 booth in Hall 6 for more details about the Full Release!
